{
  "video_id": "yr49wHVa8eM",
  "title": "How to revive public healthcare | The Economist",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 5400.0,
      "end_time": 7580.0,
      "text": "This year Britain's National Health"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 7580.0,
      "end_time": 10330.0,
      "text": "Service celebrates its 70th birthday."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10910.0,
      "end_time": 13930.0,
      "text": "Formed in 1948, it was the first state"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13930.0,
      "end_time": 15493.0,
      "text": "health service in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16680.0,
      "end_time": 20130.0,
      "text": "Today, the modern NHS is almost unrecognizable"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 20130.0,
      "end_time": 23480.0,
      "text": "from the one that was created 70 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23480.0,
      "end_time": 25800.0,
      "text": "It's the world's fifth biggest employer"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25800.0,
      "end_time": 29280.0,
      "text": "with a budget of 110 billion pounds a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29280.0,
      "end_time": 32430.0,
      "text": "But it's in urgent need of treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36740.0,
      "end_time": 39325.0,
      "text": "Like many healthcare systems, the NHS is faced"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39325.0,
      "end_time": 42963.0,
      "text": "with a funding shortfall and critical staff shortages"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42963.0,
      "end_time": 45173.0,
      "text": "meaning its future looks perilous."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46200.0,
      "end_time": 48362.0,
      "text": "Lord Ara Darzi is one of the world's top surgeons"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48362.0,
      "end_time": 51200.0,
      "text": "and a former British Health Minister."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51200.0,
      "end_time": 54580.0,
      "text": "He's been on the healthcare frontline for three decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54580.0,
      "end_time": 57583.0,
      "text": "And he's come up with a plan for reviving the NHS."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58580.0,
      "end_time": 60513.0,
      "text": "These are my talking points."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65990.0,
      "end_time": 67580.0,
      "text": "The government needs to transform the NHS from"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67580.0,
      "end_time": 70530.0,
      "text": "a sickness service to a health and wellbeing service."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70530.0,
      "end_time": 74550.0,
      "text": "Most of the chronic disease is related to human behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74550.0,
      "end_time": 77250.0,
      "text": "The NHS spends almost nine billion pounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77250.0,
      "end_time": 79338.0,
      "text": "a year dealing with diseases related to smoking"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79338.0,
      "end_time": 82210.0,
      "text": "and the growing obesity epidemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82210.0,
      "end_time": 84720.0,
      "text": "To cut costs, the government needs to tackle"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84720.0,
      "end_time": 87970.0,
      "text": "this public health crisis at its root."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87970.0,
      "end_time": 89370.0,
      "text": "We do this in three ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89370.0,
      "end_time": 92870.0,
      "text": "One, regulation, banning smoking was"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92870.0,
      "end_time": 94390.0,
      "text": "a wonderful example of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94390.0,
      "end_time": 96230.0,
      "text": "Second, taxation."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96230.0,
      "end_time": 99430.0,
      "text": "Introducing sugar tax, or a levy on alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99430.0,
      "end_time": 101360.0,
      "text": "Thirdly, behavioral intervention."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101360.0,
      "end_time": 103793.0,
      "text": "How do we help people make the right choices?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108800.0,
      "end_time": 110858.0,
      "text": "We need to embrace innovation whether that is digital"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110858.0,
      "end_time": 113675.0,
      "text": "which has transformed every aspect of our life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113675.0,
      "end_time": 115910.0,
      "text": "we need to do the same in health."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115910.0,
      "end_time": 118750.0,
      "text": "The NHS is still running on paper and fax."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118750.0,
      "end_time": 122180.0,
      "text": "We need to move from that archaic times"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122180.0,
      "end_time": 124530.0,
      "text": "into the new times of digital."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124930.0,
      "end_time": 127516.0,
      "text": "The NHS is the world's largest purchaser"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 127516.0,
      "end_time": 130420.0,
      "text": "of fax machines and in some hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130419.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133980.0,
      "text": "medical equipment is no longer fit for purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133980.0,
      "end_time": 136697.0,
      "text": "A recent report found that machines from the 1980s"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136698.0,
      "end_time": 139810.0,
      "text": "were still in use in NHS hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139810.0,
      "end_time": 142790.0,
      "text": "We need to decommission the old stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142790.0,
      "end_time": 146270.0,
      "text": "and save money to pay for the new innovations."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146270.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "Robotics, new drugs, new interventions."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151709.0,
      "text": "We need to look at frugal innovations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 151710.0,
      "end_time": 154950.0,
      "text": "technologies that are exceptionally cheap"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154950.0,
      "end_time": 158250.0,
      "text": "but at the same time delivering as good an outcome"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158250.0,
      "end_time": 159953.0,
      "text": "from a patient's perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164300.0,
      "end_time": 166959.0,
      "text": "In the 21st century, data is the energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 166959.0,
      "end_time": 169840.0,
      "text": "or the fuel of transformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 169840.0,
      "end_time": 172470.0,
      "text": "Anything you could measure you can improve"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172470.0,
      "end_time": 175490.0,
      "text": "and data is one of the ways of doing that."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 175490.0,
      "end_time": 179578.0,
      "text": "One million people use the NHS every 36 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 179578.0,
      "end_time": 182420.0,
      "text": "But there's no centralized system where doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 182420.0,
      "end_time": 184809.0,
      "text": "can access their medical data."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 184810.0,
      "end_time": 188400.0,
      "text": "Most patients seeing me expect me to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 188400.0,
      "end_time": 190250.0,
      "text": "all the data from their general practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 190250.0,
      "end_time": 192500.0,
      "text": "We need to drive this integration between"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 192500.0,
      "end_time": 196150.0,
      "text": "primary care, hospital, and back into the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 196150.0,
      "end_time": 199450.0,
      "text": "You can actually predict disease before you see"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199450.0,
      "end_time": 202959.0,
      "text": "the manifestation of disease by segmenting the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 202960.0,
      "end_time": 205880.0,
      "text": "and identifying those at great risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 205880.0,
      "end_time": 208210.0,
      "text": "To do this, the NHS will have to tackle"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 208210.0,
      "end_time": 211280.0,
      "text": "fears over personal data being shared."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211280.0,
      "end_time": 215700.0,
      "text": "Sharing data is critical from a patient's perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 215700.0,
      "end_time": 218550.0,
      "text": "And we need to win the confidence of the public when it"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 218560.0,
      "end_time": 222173.0,
      "text": "comes to the privacy and security aspect of data sharing."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227900.0,
      "end_time": 229637.0,
      "text": "The NHS is facing a funding gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 229637.0,
      "end_time": 234637.0,
      "text": "By 2020, it's estimated to be 20 billion pounds short."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235520.0,
      "end_time": 238273.0,
      "text": "A lot of people out there think investing in healthcare"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 238273.0,
      "end_time": 240303.0,
      "text": "is in a bottomless pit."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241140.0,
      "end_time": 243773.0,
      "text": "I could confidently tell you, not just my work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243773.0,
      "end_time": 245880.0,
      "text": "look at the work of the Lancet Commission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 245880.0,
      "end_time": 248299.0,
      "text": "the World Innovation Summit for Healthcare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248300.0,
      "end_time": 251160.0,
      "text": "the best return on investment any country"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 251160.0,
      "end_time": 253520.0,
      "text": "could make is in health."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 253520.0,
      "end_time": 256490.0,
      "text": "Healthy nation means a productive nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 256490.0,
      "end_time": 259100.0,
      "text": "Healthy nation means economic growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259100.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260773.00000000003,
      "text": "For every pound you spend in health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 260773.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262443.0,
      "text": "you get two pounds back."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 265990.0,
      "end_time": 268700.0,
      "text": "Quality should be the organizing principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 268700.0,
      "end_time": 271700.0,
      "text": "of any health system."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271700.0,
      "end_time": 273462.0,
      "text": "It's a wonderful future if we embrace it."
    }
  ]
}